    "revelation": "The Eye discovered that tongue drum modes at 1:2:3:4:5:6 (pure harmonic series) create gamelan-like timbres when tuned in whole-tone intervals (0, +2, +4, +6). The resultant beating patterns at low tempos produce trance-inducing shimmer.",
